title: Large, clean and bright 2 bedroom apartment for rent
posting_body: ['This is a private room in a re-furbished home.', 'The home has been built, and designed for communal living.', 'Tenants share bathrooms, laundry machines and a common kitchen.', 'The bathrooms, and common areas are cleaned weekly by the management company.', 'All tenants clean up after themselves as part of their requirements under the lease.', 'There is a communal kitchen on the first floor, and a shared bathroom on each floor.', 'Rent is', '$850/Month Rent is Due on the first Monday of every month, or every Friday if you choose to pay weekly.', 'No security deposit is due.', 'The bathroom and common area are cleaned Bi-weekly by the management company.', 'If you are interested please send me your number.', 'I will contact you soon.']
